  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK921">
<l>uṭkap paṭāa roḷiyiḻappa reññāṉṟuṅ </l>
<l>kaṭkātal koṇṭoḻuku vār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who always thirst after drink will neither inspire fear (in others) nor retain the light (of their fame).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
